data.description: Offers Due Tuesday Feb 27th 5pm. This lovely colonial is located in a cozy neighborhood and ready for the next family to enjoy! Enter the first floor to a stunning living room that flows into a dream of a kitchen and dining area! And if you are looking for the convenience of a bedroom and a bath on the first floor this home has it! There are four generous bedrooms in total with an en-suite for the primary. And bonus space in the lower level with pool table and entertainment area make this living space worth staying home for! Looking for a fenced in back yard? This home has it! Come take a look at all that this home has to offer this weekend at the open houses! Seller is building new construction and is looking to time this sale with its completion in early March.
